### Aegis ground API — vendors + pickups
### Run with REST Client extension. Replace cookie after sign-in.

@host = http://localhost:3000
@cookie = better-auth.session_token=...replace_after_signin...
@personId = REPLACE_WITH_ARTIST_OR_CREW_ID

### ── Vendors (global, no edition scoping) ──────────────────────────

### List vendors
GET {{host}}/api/vendors
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Create vendor — success
POST {{host}}/api/vendors
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "name": "Byblos Taxi",
  "service": "Taxi",
  "contactName": "Joseph",
  "contactEmail": "joseph@example.com",
  "contactPhone": "+961 1 234567"
}

### Create vendor — failure: missing service
POST {{host}}/api/vendors
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "name": "X" }

### Get vendor
@vendorId = REPLACE_WITH_VENDOR_ID
GET {{host}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Update vendor — partial
PATCH {{host}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "contactPhone": "+961 1 999999" }

### Delete vendor
DELETE {{host}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### ── Pickups (per edition) ────────────────────────────────────────

### List pickups
GET {{host}}/api/pickups
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Filter: airport runs only
GET {{host}}/api/pickups?routeFrom=airport
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Filter by status + vendor
GET {{host}}/api/pickups?status=scheduled&vendorId={{vendorId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Create pickup — success
POST {{host}}/api/pickups
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "personKind": "artist",
  "personId": "{{personId}}",
  "routeFrom": "airport",
  "routeFromDetail": "Beirut, Terminal A",
  "routeTo": "hotel",
  "routeToDetail": "Byblos Sur Mer",
  "pickupDt": "2026-08-13T15:00:00Z",
  "vehicleType": "Sedan",
  "vendorId": "{{vendorId}}",
  "driverName": "Sami",
  "driverPhone": "+961 1 234567",
  "costAmountCents": 8000,
  "costCurrency": "USD",
  "status": "scheduled"
}

### Create pickup — failure: bad route enum
POST {{host}}/api/pickups
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "personKind": "artist",
  "personId": "{{personId}}",
  "routeFrom": "moon",
  "routeTo": "hotel",
  "pickupDt": "2026-08-13T15:00:00Z"
}

### Get pickup
@pickupId = REPLACE_WITH_PICKUP_ID
GET {{host}}/api/pickups/{{pickupId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### Patch — partial: mark dispatched
PATCH {{host}}/api/pickups/{{pickupId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "status": "dispatched" }

### Patch — partial: clear vendorId
PATCH {{host}}/api/pickups/{{pickupId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{ "vendorId": "" }

### Patch — empty body (400)
PATCH {{host}}/api/pickups/{{pickupId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{}

### Delete pickup
DELETE {{host}}/api/pickups/{{pickupId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}
